                        <a href="/questions/4282413/sort-array-of-objects-by-one-property" dir="ltr">Sort array of objects by one property</a>
                            <span class="question-originals-answer-count">
                                (23 answers)
                            </span>
                    </div>
                <div class="flex--item mb0 mt8">Closed <span title="2025-02-16 19:21:12Z" class="relativetime">3 months ago</span>.</div>
        </div>
</aside>

    </div>

<p>I want to sort my object array by date, which is like that:</p>
<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$array</span> = <span class="hljs-keyword">array</span>( 
[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = <span class="hljs-keyword">array</span> (<span class="hljs-string">'date'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'2012-05-15'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'name'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'jon'</span>)
[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-keyword">array</span> (<span class="hljs-string">'date'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'2012-05-10'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'name'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'jon'</span>)
[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>] = <span class="hljs-keyword">array</span> (<span class="hljs-string">'date'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'2012-05-09'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'name'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'jon'</span>)
[<span class="hljs-number">3</span>] = <span class="hljs-keyword">array</span> (<span class="hljs-string">'date'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'2012-05-16'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'name'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'jon'</span>)
);
</code></pre>
<p>What method should I use?</p>
